Test Corpus Attribution
=======================

The test codestreams in this directory are used solely for JPEG 2000
decoder conformance testing and regression testing.

1. ITU-T T.803 Conformance Test Data (p0_*.j2k, p1_*.j2k)
   ---------------------------------------------------------
   These files are JPEG 2000 Part 4 (ITU-T T.803 | ISO/IEC 15444-4)
   conformance test codestreams. They were originally created by
   multiple organizations for the purpose of conformance testing of
   JPEG 2000 implementations.

   Distributed via: https://github.com/uclouvain/openjpeg-data
   Subdirectory:    input/conformance/

   These files are provided for conformance testing of JPEG 2000
   standard implementations per their original intended purpose.

2. Nonregression Test Data
   -----------------------
   The following files are from the openjpeg-data nonregression test dataset:
   - a1_mono.j2c, a2_colr.j2c, b1_mono.j2c, g1_colr.j2c
     (Subdirectory: input/nonregression/)
   - Bretagne1_ht.j2k, Bretagne1_ht_lossy.j2k, byte.jph, byte_causal.jhc
     (Subdirectory: input/nonregression/htj2k/)

   Distributed via: https://github.com/uclouvain/openjpeg-data

